        <section class="teacher-content">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12">
                        <h1>Introducing your INTO Newcastle teachers  </h1>
                        <p>The teachers at INTO Newcastle are here to help you reach your potential and  progress successfully to university. With a dedication and passion for teaching international students, they'll create an engaging environment for you to learn in.</p>
<p>Your teachers will give you the confidence to speak and present, write essays and discuss academic topics in English. They'll also encourage you to work independently and manage your own study time. So you know you'll be prepared for student life at a top UK university. At INTO Newcastle you're learning environment includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>cutting-edge teaching rooms with interactive screens</li>
<li>purpose-built Architecture studio and fully-equipped science labs</li>
<li>two large university-style lecture theatres</li>
<li>specially designed study spaces</li>
</ul>

                    </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                            
